  "description": "The two-chamber refrigerator of the iQ500 series is an advanced model in the line of the Siemens trademark. Due to the width increased to 70 cm with a height of 203 cm, the device has good capacity: the useful volume is 435 liters, which should be enough even for a family of 4 to 5 people. Ease of operation is provided by an external touch panel with child protection, and simplicity and ease of maintenance is provided by the Full No Frost automatic defrost system. The Siemens KG49NAI31 refrigerator received 2 cooling circuits and is characterized by economical energy consumption — up to 303 kWh (class A ++). The 330-litre fridge compartment includes a hyperFresh Box and a hanging metal rack to hold bottles. The 105-liter freezer is notable for powerful freezing (up to 15 kg per day). It is divided into 3 compartments by sliding transparent boxes. Other features of the model include a moderate noise level (up to 40 dB), the presence of a door closing indicator and an antiFingerprint coating that prevents fingerprints from appearing on the front surfaces of the case.",
